---

```sh
PYTHONPATH=./src python -m myke --myke-file tests/resources/Mykefile -h

PYTHONPATH=./src ./tests/resources/Mykefile --myke-help
```


## Build

```sh
myke py-mkdocs
```

## Deploy

```sh
myke stack-up
```
